Sure.

20:00.742 --> 20:03.328
Hope the parents aren't gonna be
too much of an impediment on this.

20:03.411 --> 20:06.164
I don't wanna step on anyone's toes here,
but time really is of the essence.

20:06.247 --> 20:08.082
The second he is declared dead,
we need to start.

20:09.125 --> 20:10.960
Is this what you're using to freeze him?

20:11.044 --> 20:13.796
We don't freeze anyone.
We're gonna vitrify him.

20:14.589 --> 20:17.050
We replace his blood
with a medicalâ€“grade antifreeze.

20:17.133 --> 20:19.886
As soon as his body temp hits
