20:24.974 --> 20:26.059
Takes about three hours.

20:26.142 --> 20:28.144
You paged me?
Yeah.

20:28.227 --> 20:29.520
The parents wanted to speak with you.

20:32.649 --> 20:34.567
Mr. and Mrs. Shepard? Please.

20:36.319 --> 20:37.528
This is Dr. Charles.

20:37.612 --> 20:39.739
Why is no one stopping my boy
from doing this?

20:39.822 --> 20:41.115
Todd just turned 18.

20:41.199 --> 20:42.825
He can't make a decision
like this for himself.

20:42.909 --> 20:44.202
(ALARM BLARING)

20:44.994 --> 20:46.412
He's bradying down.

20:46.496 --> 20:47.705
What's that?

20:47.789 --> 20:50.083
His heart stopped.
Well, do something!

20:50.166 --> 20:51.918
I'm not legally authorized to.
BEA: Please!

20:53.002 --> 20:54.629
We only have so much time left with him!

20:54.712 --> 20:55.713
Well, we're not ready for him to die yet.

21:00.593 --> 21:03.930
Have you noticed any personality changes
in Shep since the diagnosis?

21:04.013 --> 21:05.014
I don't know...

21:06.265 --> 21:09.227
Has he been more impetuous, stubborn,
less willing to listen to reason?

21:11.562 --> 21:12.730
Yes, of course.

21:12.814 --> 21:14.607
I'm deeming the patient
decisionally incapacitated.

21:14.691 --> 21:17.527
As next of kin, you have the right
to make medical decisions on his behalf.

21:17.610 --> 21:19.070
Should we attempt to resuscitate him?
Yes! Do it!

21:19.153 --> 21:20.947
All right, get me a crash cart.
Start bagging!

21:22.407 --> 21:24.325
Quickâ€“look paddles.
Hey, give us some room!

21:33.543 --> 21:36.004
How long will he need to stay on support?

21:36.087 --> 21:39.132
Until the drugs work through his system.
A few more hours at least.

21:40.049 --> 21:41.050
Thank you, Doctor.

21:41.926 --> 21:42.927
Sure.

21:46.931 --> 21:48.307
Guess you guys rushed here for nothing.

21:49.475 --> 21:52.520
Well, transfer's already paid for,
so, we'll stand by, if it's all the same,

21:52.603 --> 21:53.604
just in case.

21:56.357 --> 21:57.900
You can hang in that room
for the time being.

22:00.486 --> 22:03.156
I didn't think you were
buying my personality change argument.

22:03.239 --> 22:06.075
Just erring on the side
of caution, you know?

22:06.159 --> 22:07.452
Give everybody a little more time.

22:07.535 --> 22:08.870
You made the right call.
CAROLINE: Thank you.

22:08.953 --> 22:10.747
I hope so.
So, what?

22:10.830 --> 22:13.833
You forbade me
from having the surgery? Really?

22:13.916 --> 22:16.169
So we get married and now I have to ask
for permission for stuff?

22:16.252 --> 22:18.129
Is that right?
I wasn't...

22:18.212 --> 22:19.213
Come here, come here.

22:22.467 --> 22:23.843
I'm not forbidding anything.

22:23.926 --> 22:25.303
I just want to make sure
that we have enough time

22:25.386 --> 22:26.804
to think this through.
I've thought about it.

22:26.888 --> 22:28.806
I want the surgery.
For a Baked Alaska?

22:28.890 --> 22:30.266
Yes.
Do you know how crazy that sounds?

22:30.349 --> 22:31.809
It's not about the Baked Alaska.

22:32.685 --> 22:35.980
It's about me showing love to the people
I care about the way I want to.

22:36.064 --> 22:37.648
Look, I know I'm not
the best cook in the world,

22:37.732 --> 22:39.233
but I can figure out a whisk.
I'll help you.

22:39.317 --> 22:41.110
No. No. No.
We'll do it together.

22:41.194 --> 22:42.195
No!

22:43.071 --> 22:46.199
Time is precious, Daniel,
and I don't wanna spend four weeks

22:46.282 --> 22:48.201
not being able to use my hand.

22:49.452 --> 22:51.287
You knew who I was
when you signed on for this.

22:51.370 --> 22:52.497
You knew who I was.

22:52.580 --> 22:55.833
No, this isn't what I signed up for.
You being reckless with your health.

22:55.917 --> 22:56.918
That wasn't the deal.

22:57.668 --> 22:58.961
There's too much to lose here.

22:59.045 --> 23:00.505
I think you're being a little selfish.

23:00.588 --> 23:02.048
So, now I'm being selfish. Really?

23:02.131 --> 23:03.800
I mean, I just found you again.

23:03.883 --> 23:05.718
I wanna have as much time
with you as possible.

23:05.802 --> 23:07.637
And I'm kinda hoping
you feel the same way.

23:07.720 --> 23:09.430
I do, but you know what?
This is my choice.

23:09.514 --> 23:11.057
Period. You hear that?

23:12.266 --> 23:13.267
Period.

23:16.145 --> 23:17.355
(ELEVATOR BELL DINGS)

23:17.438 --> 23:20.608
I tried to get her to let us
examine her, but she refused,

23:20.691 --> 23:22.902
and given the circumstances
of the delivery...

23:22.985 --> 23:25.404
No. You did the right thing
calling Child Services, April.

23:25.488 --> 23:26.489
