about her baby, so, I gave her Ativan.

23:41.170 --> 23:42.839
Should wear off in an hour or so.

23:42.922 --> 23:45.299
Melissa, will you notify us
when she wakes up?

23:45.383 --> 23:46.551
Of course.
Thank you.

23:49.595 --> 23:52.265
I cannot believe that you would
undermine me like that.

23:52.348 --> 23:53.349
Excuse me?

23:53.432 --> 23:55.518
You knew I was calling DCFS in
to talk to her.

23:55.601 --> 23:57.186
You sedated her on purpose.

23:57.270 --> 23:58.312
Please.

23:58.396 --> 24:02.400
You know what, you don't wanna help? Fine.
Just do me a favor, stay out of my way.

24:10.408 --> 24:12.160
Goodwin got you a lackey?

24:13.661 --> 24:16.581
What'd you do
to get such special treatment?

24:16.664 --> 24:19.584
I'm just training her, Doris.
It's not permanent.

24:19.667 --> 24:20.710
That's not what I heard.

24:21.752 --> 24:22.753
Huh.

24:23.421 --> 24:25.006
Good thing I checked these.

24:25.089 --> 24:26.632
Look how many had almost expired.
(SIGHS)

24:26.716 --> 24:28.801
You know, if you want, I could
